<div class="about-page">

  {%- comment -%} ══════ HERO ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero-visual">
      <img src="{{ 'br-hero-about.webp' | asset_url }}"
           alt="A polished amethyst gua sha stone resting on folded cream linen, surrounded by half-used skincare bottles in warm morning light"
           loading="eager"
           width="1920" height="1072">
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-content">
      <h1 class="about-title">I tried every serum.<br><span class="about-title-accent">Then I tried a stone.</span></h1>
      <p class="about-hero-sub">A short, honest version of how this brand exists &mdash; and why I built it around four tools instead of forty bottles.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ══════ THE THING I THOUGHT I WAS MISSING ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-grid">
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <p>For ten years, I did what the wellness aisle told me. I bought the vitamin C. The retinol. The peptide creams in $60 jars with names that sounded like a chemistry lab. Some of them did something. Most of them sat on the surface of my skin while I just hoped.</p>
        <p class="about-section-emphasis">Hope, it turns out, is a terrible morning routine.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section-visual">
        <img src="{{ 'br-about-shelf.webp' | asset_url }}"
             alt="A row of unbranded skincare bottles in muted glass on a bathroom shelf, cold morning light"
             loading="lazy"
             width="1536" height="1920">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ══════ TAIPEI, 2023 ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--reversed about-section--cream-dark">
    <div class="about-section-grid">
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <span class="section-label">Taipei, 2023</span>
        <p>A friend in Taipei handed me a curved piece of amethyst the size of a deck of cards. <em>Five minutes. Every morning. That&rsquo;s it.</em></p>
        <p>I laughed. I had a bathroom full of $50 bottles. A rock wasn&rsquo;t going to outperform them.</p>
        <p class="about-section-emphasis">Three weeks later, people started asking if I&rsquo;d lost weight. I hadn&rsquo;t.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section-visual">
        <img src="{{ 'br-about-taipei.webp' | asset_url }}"
             alt="Two hands meeting in soft afternoon light, one offering a polished amethyst gua sha stone, the other reaching to receive it"
             loading="lazy"
             width="1920" height="1280">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ══════ WHY A STONE DOES WHAT A SERUM CAN'T ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-grid">
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">Why a stone does <em>what a serum can&rsquo;t.</em></h2>
        <p>Skincare works on chemistry. Active molecules diffuse into the upper layers of skin and, sometimes, reach the cells they&rsquo;re aimed at. That&rsquo;s the absorption model. It&rsquo;s real, but it&rsquo;s slow, narrow, and dependent on getting past a barrier your body designed to keep things out.</p>
        <p>Tools work on physics. Pressure, glide, and cold change three things creams cannot reach: how lymph fluid distributes, how fascia holds tension, and how blood circulates near the surface.</p>
        <p class="about-section-emphasis">A serum changes what&rsquo;s <em>in</em> your skin. A stone changes what your skin is <em>doing.</em></p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section-visual">
        <img src="{{ 'br-about-cheek.webp' | asset_url }}"
             alt="A polished amethyst gua sha stone gliding along the curve of a cheek and jawline in soft natural light"
             loading="lazy"
             width="1536" height="1920">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ══════ THEN WHY DOESN'T EVERY BRAND SELL THEM ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-section about-section--reversed about-section--cream-dark">
    <div class="about-section-grid">
      <div class="about-section-text">
        <h2 class="about-section-title">Then why doesn&rsquo;t <em>every brand</em> sell them?</h2>
        <p>Honest answer: tools are not a great business.</p>
        <p>A serum gets used up. A stone doesn&rsquo;t. Bottles repeat-purchase every six weeks; a polished piece of amethyst will outlive everyone in the house. The skincare industry didn&rsquo;t build tools because the math doesn&rsquo;t work. It built bottles because the math does.</p>
        <p class="about-section-emphasis">I built BY RITUEL anyway. I made the tools I&rsquo;d wanted, in the materials and shapes I&rsquo;d looked for and couldn&rsquo;t find at a price that didn&rsquo;t insult anyone.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section-visual">
        <img src="{{ 'br-about-amethyst.webp' | asset_url }}"
             alt="A cluster of raw, uncut amethyst crystals on cream linen &mdash; the material before it becomes a tool"
             loading="lazy"
             width="1920" height="1072">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ══════ QUIET EMAIL SIGNUP ══════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="about-signup">
    <div class="about-signup-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Stay in touch</span>
      <h2 class="about-signup-title">A few emails <em>a year.</em></h2>
      <p class="about-signup-desc">When I release something new, or write a technique guide worth reading, I&rsquo;ll send it. No marketing, no urgency, no spam. Unsubscribe in one click.</p>
      <div class="about-signup-form">
        <div class="klaviyo-form-TpBtCX"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

<style>
.about-page {
  --brand-cream: var(--cream, #F7F2EA);
  --brand-cream-dark: var(--cream-dark, #EDE6D6);
  --brand-espresso: var(--espresso, #1E120A);
  --brand-stone: var(--stone, #6B5A40);
  --brand-terracotta: var(--terracotta, #A15E3C);
  --brand-blush: var(--blush, #E8C5B0);
  background: var(--brand-cream);
  overflow: hidden;
  color: var(--brand-espresso);
}

.about-page .section-label {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.32em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--brand-terracotta);
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

/* ── HERO ── */
.about-hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 1fr;
  min-height: 88vh;
  padding-top: 88px;
}
.about-hero-visual {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  min-height: 540px;
}
.about-hero-visual img {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  filter: saturate(0.94) contrast(1.02);
}
.about-hero-content {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 80px clamp(32px, 6vw, 110px);
}
.about-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(40px, 5.4vw, 84px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.02;
  letter-spacing: -0.015em;
  color: var(--brand-espresso);
  margin: 0 0 36px;
}
.about-title-accent {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brand-terracotta);
}
.about-hero-sub {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 18px);
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--brand-stone);
  max-width: 46ch;
  margin: 0;
  font-style: italic;
}

/* ── NARRATIVE SECTIONS ── */
.about-section {
  padding: clamp(80px, 12vh, 150px) clamp(32px, 6vw, 100px);
  background: var(--brand-cream);
}
.about-section--cream-dark {
  background: var(--brand-cream-dark);
}
.about-section--final {
  padding-bottom: clamp(120px, 16vh, 200px);
}
.about-section-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: clamp(48px, 6vw, 96px);
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-section--reversed .about-section-grid {
  grid-template-areas: "visual text";
}
.about-section--reversed .about-section-text { grid-area: text; }
.about-section--reversed .about-section-visual { grid-area: visual; }

.about-section-text p {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(19px, 1.55vw, 24px);
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--brand-espresso);
  margin: 0 0 22px;
  font-weight: 300;
}
.about-section-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

.about-section-emphasis {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brand-terracotta) !important;
  font-size: clamp(21px, 1.85vw, 28px) !important;
  line-height: 1.4 !important;
  font-weight: 400 !important;
  margin-top: 28px !important;
}
.about-section-emphasis em { font-style: italic; }

.about-section-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 52px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.08;
  color: var(--brand-espresso);
  margin: 0 0 32px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.about-section-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brand-terracotta);
}

.about-section-visual {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
.about-section-visual img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
  filter: saturate(0.94) contrast(1.02);
  transition: transform 1.4s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1);
}

/* ── QUIET EMAIL SIGNUP ── */
.about-signup {
  background: var(--brand-cream);
  padding: clamp(100px, 14vh, 180px) clamp(32px, 6vw, 100px);
  text-align: center;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(30, 18, 10, 0.08);
}
.about-signup-inner {
  max-width: 580px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-signup .section-label {
  color: var(--brand-terracotta);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.about-signup-title {
  font-family: var(--serif);
  font-size: clamp(32px, 3.6vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--brand-espresso);
  margin: 0 0 22px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.about-signup-title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brand-terracotta);
}
.about-signup-desc {
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: clamp(14px, 1.1vw, 16px);
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--brand-stone);
  margin: 0 0 36px;
}
.about-signup-form {
  max-width: 440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.about-signup-form .klaviyo-form-TpBtCX form {
  background: transparent !important;
}

/* ── SCROLL-REVEAL ── */
.about-section { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1); }
.about-section.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.about-section.is-visible .about-section-visual img { transform: scale(1.02); }
.about-signup { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1), transform 0.9s cubic-bezier(.16,1,.3,1); }
.about-signup.is-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-hero {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    min-height: auto;
    padding-top: 72px;
  }
  .about-hero-visual {
    min-height: 0;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 2;
  }
  .about-hero-content {
    padding: 56px 24px 72px;
  }
  .about-section {
    padding: 64px 24px;
  }
  .about-section-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
  }
  .about-section--reversed .about-section-grid {
    grid-template-areas: "text" "visual";
  }
  .about-signup {
    padding: 80px 24px 96px;
  }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .about-section,
  .about-signup,
  .about-section-visual img {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    transform: none !important;
    transition: none !important;
  }
}
</style>

<script>
  (function () {
    var sections = document.querySelectorAll('.about-section, .about-signup');
    if (!sections.length || typeof IntersectionObserver === 'undefined') {
      sections.forEach(function (s) { s.classList.add('is-visible'); });
      return;
    }
    var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
          io.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.15, rootMargin: '0px 0px -50px 0px' });
    sections.forEach(function (s) { io.observe(s); });
  })();
</script>

